Rating: 2
I made this recipe with no changes and was a bit dissapointed with the results. It was easy to make, but the crust, pecans, and caramel sauce totally overwhelmed the very good peach ice cream I used. The other flavors are great, but I was expecting to taste peach too. I'd just use vanilla next time.

